import React from 'react';
import Cards from './Cards' 
import Data from './data';
import Heading from './Heading';
import './index.css'
let srcc = "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/38/Stranger_Things_logo.png"
function App(){
    return (<>

        <Heading/>
        <Cards nam = {Data[0].nam} imsSrc = {srcc} comapny = "Netflix" />
        <Cards nam = {Data[1].nam} imsSrc = {srcc}  comapny = "Amazon"/>
        <Cards nam = {Data[2].nam} imsSrc = {srcc}  comapny = "Disney"/>
        <Cards nam = {Data[2].nam} imsSrc = {srcc}  comapny = "Disney"/>
        <Cards nam = {Data[2].nam} imsSrc = {srcc}  comapny = "Disney"/>
        
        </>)
}
export default App
